常单手握持的兵器。最常见的短兵器是刀和剑。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-230f043f79cbab7687ef0514e07efd13_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "54 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/617850523"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4Ik/Lh4NerxsJLEAMaCDk5NTgwMzA4IIDP+KYGMAA4N0Agcgk2MTc4NTA1MjN4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "33_1694520568.755189", "card_id": "Q_621645954", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 19}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "海淀区房管局回应「网传北京解除二手房指导价限制」，称「可按市场价格对外展示房源」，将带来哪些影响？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "据媒体报道，北京市海淀区 29 个小区的二手房交易指导参考价已取消。对此，北京市海淀区房管局工作人员示，目前进行动态调整，可以按照正常的市场价格对外展示房源信息。有房地产中介机构人士表示，「自上周五（9 月 8 日）起，可以根据市场价格挂牌展示，指导价是否解除以官方为准」。北京解除二手房指导价限制？海淀区房管局：可按市场价格对外展示房源 | 界面新闻 · 快讯"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-0dba4285c4eb1f92f170d9d88b183dd5_1440w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "54 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/621645954"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Ik/Lh4NerxsJLEAMaCTEwMDQyMzIyMiDlvf+nBjAAOEZAIXIJNjIxNjQ1OTU0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "34_1694520568.756021", "card_id": "Q_620912700", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 29}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "你面临过艰难的职业选择吗？回头看你想对当时的自己说什么？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "如题"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "54 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/620912700"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Ik/Lh4NerxsJLEAMaCTEwMDI2MDIzNiCl9eWnBjAAODFAInIJNjIwOTEyNzAweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "